sequenceDiagram
    participant Auto as auto.ts 主循环
    participant State as state.ts 状态读取
    participant Dispatch as auto-dispatch.ts 规则表
    participant Rule1 as check-crash-recovery
    participant Rule2 as check-budget-ceiling
    participant RuleN as execute-next-task
    participant Prompt as auto-prompts.ts

    Auto->>State: deriveState(basePath)
    State-->>Auto: GSDState
    Auto->>Dispatch: evaluateRules(ctx)
    Dispatch->>Rule1: match(ctx)
    Rule1-->>Dispatch: null（无崩溃）
    Dispatch->>Rule2: match(ctx)
    Rule2-->>Dispatch: null（预算正常）
    Dispatch->>RuleN: match(ctx)
    RuleN-->>Dispatch: {action:"dispatch", unitType:"execute-task"}
    Dispatch-->>Auto: DispatchAction
    Auto->>Prompt: buildExecuteTaskPrompt(...)
    Prompt-->>Auto: 构建好的 Prompt